9cac83a11f82082ef21?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dlwade%26avatarId%3D11103%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Lester Wade","active":true,"timeZone":"Europe/London"},"created":"2012-10-03T10:29:18.283-0500","updated":"2012-10-03T10:29:18.283-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/16151/comment/33106","id":"33106","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=mdlr","name":"mdlr","key":"mdlr","accountId":"557058:29fd1eba-b820-4c8d-9228-0f52cb260d76","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Michael De La Rue","active":false,"timeZone":"Europe/Berlin"},"body":"There are some real dangers with this approach and I think it should be done very carefully.  I also think that the same aims can be achieved otherwise.  I've created EUCA-3680 to explain what I understand is needed.  \r\n\r\nDangers include\r\n* Two users end up wanting to restore the same instance ID from different times; one or the other fails.\r\n* An instance ID gets used up by a new user before the restore takes place\r\n\r\nHaving said that, it's pretty clear from [Amazon handling of outages|http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/07/03/amazon_outage_post_mortem/] that they are able to restore instance IDs.  \r\n\r\nFor this feature to be implmentable I think:\r\n\r\n* instance IDs need to be guaranteed unique over all time on a given cloud (use [GUID|http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Globally_unique_identifier] or a permanent record file with all past instances) \r\n* proper care and security takes place (simple DOS attack: I restore my instance on your ID before you have a chance to restore yours;  your system fails to recover).  ","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=mdlr","name":"mdlr","key":"mdlr","accountId":"557058:29fd1eba-b820-4c8d-9228-0f52cb260d76","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/15f3c4b7a0cf758ddb400a37f09f0c86?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Michael De La Rue","active":false,"timeZone":"Europe/Berlin"},"created":"2012-10-04T04:11:18.131-0500","updated":"2012-10-04T04:11:18.131-0500"}],"maxResults":3,"total":3,"startAt":0},"customfield_11808":null,"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]}}}